As you are all aware the various presidential candidates/flag-bearers seem to have growing supporters that believe in them from the start to finish because they assume or know they are capable of transforming the country and taking it to a greater height if they are elected and giving the golden opportunity to rule as the president in 2023.
In the light of the following happenings, a staunch member of the All Progressive Congress Party APC Lagos branch, Joe Igbokwe has taken to his official Facebook page to react after Daddy Freeze says that if Tinubu wins it will be a boom for Nigerian youths.
In his Facebook post, the elder statesman uploaded a news publication by Legit.ng with the photos of Tinubu and Daddy Freeze as it indicates that was reacting to one of Asiwaju’s supporters Identified as Mr Jollof. The report however stated that the OAP made it known that if the All Progressive Congress Party APC Presidential candidate runs for the 2023 general election and emerges as the winner, it will be a massive explosion for the youths of Nigeria and the country at large.
Mr. Joe Igbokwe who seems to be a strong supporter of his principal could not say many words as he could note that the said Nigerian youths are beginning to make their voice known and heard as he affirms that he (Bola Tinubu) is friendly if you know him very much.
Guys what is your opinion on this?


